  "history": "The client has a longstanding pattern of recurring conflicts and strained relationships, often marked by trust and boundary issues. Some of these relationships have been complicated by alcoholism, which may have contributed to feelings of frustration and helplessness. There is a history of aggressive behavior, possibly as a defensive response to feeling misunderstood or threatened. The client has struggled with managing emotions and maintaining healthy boundaries, leading to cycles of conflict and withdrawal.",
